- ScalaTest

ScalaTest
- Apache 2.0
- can integrate Junit, TestNg, ScalaCheck
- Mocikto, ScalaMock, EasyMock, JMock

8 Testing Styles
- xUnit
- BDD
- RSpec
- PropSpec etc

ScalaTest is most used in Akka, sbt

To know better
- Test vs Suite
